@startuml ai-generation-flow
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 260
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #BBBBBB
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceGroupBodyBackgroundColor #F5F0FF

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #E8F0FE
  BorderColor #4A7BCC
  FontSize 14
  FontStyle bold
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  BorderColor #E0C860
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam sequence {
  DividerBackgroundColor #F0F0F0
  DividerBorderColor #CCCCCC
  DividerFontSize 13
  DividerFontStyle bold
}

title <size:16>AI Mock Generation Flow</size>

actor "User" as User
participant "Generation\nLambda" as GL
participant "Amazon\nBedrock" as LLM

User -> GL : API spec + description\n//(OpenAPI, GraphQL, or WSDL)//
activate GL #E8F0FE

== Parse & Compress ==

GL -> GL : Parse spec into\ncompact representation

== Generate ==

note right of GL
  **Generation prompt:**
  compressed spec, user description,
  WireMock schema rules, prompt template
end note

GL -> LLM : Generation prompt
activate LLM #FFF3E0
LLM --> GL : WireMock JSON mappings
deactivate LLM

== Validate ==

GL -> GL : Validate each mapping

alt #F5F0FF Invalid mocks detected

  GL -> GL : Separate valid from invalid

  note right of GL
    **Correction prompt:**
    invalid mocks + errors, spec context,
    correction template
    //LLM session retains original context//
  end note

  GL -> LLM : Correction prompt\n//(invalid mocks + errors only)//
  activate LLM #FFF3E0
  LLM --> GL : Corrected mappings
  deactivate LLM

  GL -> GL : Re-validate & merge\nwith valid originals
end

== Return ==

GL --> User : **Valid WireMock mappings only**
deactivate GL

@enduml
